target_interaction.text: I have been watching The Restaurant to keep my sessions on the treadmill from being boring. The only problem is that I am so hooked on this story - and cast - that I am spending longer and longer on the treadmill. It's hard to stop. This is an outstanding Swedish production with great views of Stockholm now and then.
